2001;;Escape from Hell;;American;;Danny Carrales;;Daniel Kruse, Emilie Jo Tisdale, Terry Jernigan;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Escape_from_Hell_(2001_film);;The film is about a man, Dr. Eric Robinson, who puts himself in cardiac arrest in order to scientifically study near-death experiences. In the course of his experiments he ventures into both heaven and hell. The film ends with the invitation to accept or reject Christ as Savior.